SHE'S ARODEOQUEEN pursued from midpack along the inside, but steadied between foes and got shuffled back behind a faltering foe at the three furlong pole, yet sustained a rail grind through the lane. LYRICAL PARDON stalked along the inside, vied around the far turn, but yielded in midstretch and faded between horses. TAKETHESILVER laid off of the pace two to three wide, chased in the four path and between horses around the far turn and gave way. ENDURING stalked two wide, vied between horses around the far turn and weakened entering the lane. BETHSHEBA laid off of the pace along the inside and failed to factor. NOTO broke a bit outwardly, pursued from midpack two wide, retreated down the backstretch, raced off of the pace in the four path around the far turn and made little impact. BERNAR MOSA tracked three wide, vied between horses around the far turn and weakened nearing the lane. THE ENEMY OF FUN broke inwardly before being hustled to the front, showed the way with a clear margin in the three to two path, but wilted between horses at the three furlong pole.
